# cBots

Collection of automated trading systems developed for cTrader Automate.

These projects focus on market analysis, risk management, trade execution and workflow automation.

## Objectives

- Trading automation
- Risk management
- Position management
- Market structure execution
- Quantitative trading models

## Projects

### Smart Flow Engine

Automated trading framework designed to evaluate market conditions using liquidity, structure and momentum.

### Trade Manager Bot

Position management utility focused on trade monitoring, risk control and execution management.

### Risk Manager Bot

Risk management system designed to calculate exposure, position sizing and capital preservation rules.

### Quantitative Execution Bot

Experimental framework for quantitative model implementation and automated market participation.

## Technologies

- C#
- cTrader Automate
- .NET

## Status

Active Development
